Originally, I was going to ask on Graffe's or some other wizard board, but I figured I'd probably get a better answer here in my own 'hood. <p>Prybutok Agonista&lt;br&gt;<br>
Last Survivor of Agony &lt;br&gt;<br>
&lt;img src=&quot;http://prybutok.homestead.com/files/Prybutokgimpysmall.jpg&quot;&gt;</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aurianne>Aurianne</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mana Whore</span><br>  Posts: 1359<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(10/24/02 5:10:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3411.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Pry...</span><hr size=1> Ask the &quot;what race&quot; question on Graffe's, and you'll get spittle-spewing, and little of substance.<br>
