<br>
As for race choice, end-game gear makes most of your stuff meaningless. Pick what you like. Personally, I liked High Elves. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=roggelmustaffafez>Roggel MustaffaFez</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.tripod.co.uk/redhotant/icons/iconoc03.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I Live Here</span><br>  Posts: 1097<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(10/24/02 6:03:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3411.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.d0ng3r.com/pics/cup14_.bmp WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Pry...</span><hr size=1> You begin casting Bonds of Force<br>
