<br>
<br>
then again, im a noob, dont ask me <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=atro>Atro</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Contributing Member</span><br>  Posts: 196<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(10/24/02 6:08:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3411.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Pry...</span><hr size=1> For leveling a new wiz equip doesn't seem to be all that important. Most normal caster gear you can find in the bazaar should be fine. Only thing I can think of that would really help is some of those new FT items, but those are rather expensive. One of those lower costs horses could be a big help.<br>
<br>
Be sure to take advantage of PC from around 16 through 26.<br>
<br>
Not really sure what to advise from 26+ - 40, various zones have nice exp bonuses, but getting good groups can be hard.<br>
After 40, do the staff of temperate flux quest, and start quadding. Grouping of course is fine 40+, but quad exp is usually just as good or better. Quadding might also work better with having to split playtime between your twink and your main.<br>
<br>
As for choice of race, I would recommend Erudite. Int is your primary stat, and regardless of where they cap int winds up, having a high natural int gives you more gear choices later on.<br>
The new Luclin / PoP port systems also negate the erudite ass starting position. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=firion69>Firion69</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Contributing Member</span><br>  Posts: 212<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(10/24/02 6:57:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3411.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Pry...</span><hr size=1> If i had the choice today, I would remake Firion Human. Hes Eru now.<br>
