<br>
I probably have less then 20k in gear and about 6 days of play time and am lvl 51 already.  If you can stand not grouping you can level your wizard fast with kei.  Quading&gt;root/blast&gt;groups.  I've grouped some lately just to break up the monotiny and its amazingly slow.  Even quading spirocs now with most of them light blue its still faster then a chain pulling group.<br>
<br>
