<br>
From 16 to 24 level in Pauldral Caverns<br>
24 to 34 level in monseru (I think) (greyhoppers, stonegrabbers ect)<br>
34 to 44 do ulthorks and walrus in east waiste (quading)<br>
44 to 51 spirocs are your friend.<br>
51 to 54 wyverns in cobalt scar if you can play during the non peak times<br>
54 to 60 raptors/goranga/toilers/shadel bandits/AE groups if you can get em around 58+<br>
<br>
<br>
Thats my plan at least and working well for me.<br>
